        <h3 class="h5"><a href="http://international.gc.ca/world-monde/study_work_travel-etude_travail_voyage/index.aspx?lang=eng">Travel the world</a></h3>
        <p>Plan your studies, work or travel abroad and in Canada.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h5"><a href="/en/services/culture/cultural-youth-programs.html">Leadership and cultural programs</a></h3>
        <p>Work experiences, internships, park activities and language immersion programs.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="clearfix visible-md"></div>
      <section class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h5"><a href="/en/services/youth/contribute.html">Contribute to your community</a></h3>
        <p>Build a better future for yourself and your community by volunteering.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h5"><a href="/en/services/finance/manage.html">Managing your money</a></h3>
        <p>Budgeting, banking, money transfers, insurance and planning your finances.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h5"><a href="/en/services/health/youth-health.html">Health</a></h3>
        <p>Facts about smoking, drugs, cybersafety, bullying, sex, mental health and more.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="clearfix visible-md"></div>
      <section class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h5"><a href="/en/services/policing/justice/youth/index.html">Youth justice</a></h3>
        <p>Learn about the youth justice system.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
